OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,FAn 'idiot' driver overtook numerous
OL,8,Fcars on the wrong side of the road
OL,9,Fwhile driving twice the speed limit -
OL,10,Fbefore crashing into an elderly
OL,11,Fcouple's vehicle killing a man.
OL,13,FCaleb Mansfield-Marr, 22, sped up to
OL,14,Fthe junction of Ashton Road and
OL,15,FLingard lane in Bredbury, Stockport,
OL,16,Fin August 2023.
OL,18,FHe was driving so quickly a woman felt
OL,19,Fher car "shake" as he drove past,
OL,20,Fwhile another driver said he was
OL,21,F"driving like an idiot".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
