OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,FAs grandparents Jack and Judith Howe
OL,8,Fturned right onto Lingard Lane,
OL,9,FMansfield-Marr crashed into them head-
OL,10,Fon.
OL,12,FMr Howe, 76, was left with serious
OL,13,Finternal injuries and died weeks
OL,14,Flater, while his wife of 50 years was
OL,15,Fleft with serious injuries, but made a
OL,16,Ffull recovery.
OL,18,FMansfield-Marr, from Hyde, was also
OL,19,Fhurt and posted a picture online of
OL,20,Fhis injuries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
