OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,FPolice later found videos on his phone
OL,8,F- including one in which he filmed
OL,9,Fhimself driving with his feet hanging
OL,10,Fout of the window.
OL,12,FHe later pleaded guilty to causing
OL,13,Fdeath by dangerous driving; causing
OL,14,Fserious injury by dangerous driving;
OL,15,Fand causing death by driving while
OL,16,Fdisqualified and without insurance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
