OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,FProsecutor Robert Smith told Minshull
OL,8,FStreet Crown COurt that at around
OL,9,F11.20am on 5 August, Mrs Howe was
OL,10,Fdriving her Toyota Aygo along Ashton
OL,11,FRoad in Bredbury when she approached
OL,12,Fthe junction with Lingard Lane. Her
OL,13,Fhusband Jack was in the passenger seat.
OL,15,FShe gave way to several cars before
OL,16,Fmaking the turn. Mansfield-Marr,
OL,17,Fdriving a VW Polo in the opposite
OL,18,Fdirection, had already overtaken two
OL,19,Fcars on the wrong side of the road at
OL,20,Fspeeds of 64mph. The road was governed
OL,21,Fby 30mph limit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
