OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,F"Had the defendant been driving at
OL,8,F30mph, Mrs Howe would have had ample
OL,9,Ftime to complete her turn without the
OL,10,Fdefendant taking any action," the
OL,11,Fprosecutor added.
OL,13,FThe VW Polo collided with the Toyota
OL,14,FAygo sending both cars spinning across
OL,15,Fthe junction. Mrs Howe was seriously
OL,16,Finjured. Nearby builders used angle
OL,17,Fgrinders and crowbars to get her out
OL,18,Fof the car. She and her husband were
OL,19,Frushed to hospital.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@]O]
