OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,FShe suffered from a number of injuries
OL,8,Fincluding a broken pelvis and ribs,
OL,9,Fand was treated and discharged after
OL,10,Feight weeks. Mr Howe suffered multiple
OL,11,Finjuries to his body. CT scans later
OL,12,Fshowed significant wounds to his
OL,13,Fspleen as well as a collapsed lung.
OL,15,FDespite the best efforts of medical
OL,16,Fstaff, he died on September 25.
OL,17,FMansfield-Marr was also injured and
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
