OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,FHe later took a picture of himself and
OL,8,Fuploaded it online with the caption:
OL,9,F"Fractured spine...chipped tooth...cut
OL,10,Fon head... old man pulled out."
OL,12,FHe was later arrested and interviewed
OL,13,Fand his phone was seized. Officers
OL,14,Ffound a number of videos in which he
OL,15,Fhad filmed himself driving.
