OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,FOne video showed him driving at 80mph
OL,8,Fin the motorway in cruise control with
OL,9,Fhis feet out of the driver's window.
OL,10,FIn another he filmed himself doing
OL,11,Fdoughnuts in a car park and another
OL,12,Fshowed him overtaking other cars.
OL,14,FSpeaking of her husband's death, Mrs
OL,15,FHowe said: "The morning of 25
OL,16,FSeptember 2023 changed my life
OL,17,Fforever, I became a widow. My lovely
OL,18,Fkind and caring husband of fifty years
OL,19,Fhad passed away. No more
OL,20,Fcompanionship, conversations, laughs
OL,21,For celebrations to share together.
OL,26,@wD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
