OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,F"I am healing from my injuries, but
OL,8,Fnothing can heal my loss of losing
OL,9,FJack, my husband and my best friend."
OL,10,FTheir son, Richard, said: "Our world
OL,11,Ffeels like a dark place without his
OL,12,Flight," he said.
OL,14,FSarah, their daughter, said she had
OL,15,Fdriven past the collision but did not
OL,16,Frealise it was her parents. "He was a
OL,17,Fkind, doting and supportive man, and
OL,18,Fsomeone I looked up to. I don't think
OL,19,FI will recover from this," she added.
