OL,7,FTheir third child, Louise, said: "Our
OL,8,Ffamily structure is fractured, we are
OL,9,Fnot able to regroup and never will -
OL,10,Fthere will always be one missing
OL,11,Fpiece."
OL,13,FThe court heard that Mansfield-Marr
OL,14,Fhad previous driving matters on his
OL,15,Frecord including for speeding and
OL,16,Ffailing to provide driver details. He
OL,17,Fwas banned at the time for six months.
