OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,FAn image later recovered from his
OL,8,Fphone showed Mansfield-Marr holding
OL,9,Fthe letter informing him he was
OL,10,Fdisqualified next to a gas hob, the
OL,11,Fcourt heard.
OL,13,FMitigating, John Dye said his client
OL,14,Fhad written multiple letters to the
OL,15,Ffamily of Mr Howe apologising for his
OL,16,Fbehaviour.
OL,18,FThe barrister said he was diagnosed
OL,19,Fwith ADHD which reflected in him
OL,20,F'acting like a teenager'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
