OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,FJudge Angela Nield, sentencing,
OL,8,Fdescribed Mansfield-Marr's driving as
OL,9,F'frankly appalling', and said: "This
OL,10,Fwas not a one off but a habit, and a
OL,11,Fhabit to be celebrated on social
OL,12,Fmedia. It was a matter of pride."
OL,14,FMansfield-Marr, of St Paul's Gardens,
OL,15,Fwas jailed for 12 years and banned
OL,16,Ffrom driving for 16 years. He will
OL,17,Fserve two thirds of the jail term
OL,18,Fbefore being released on licence.
