OL,7,FPS Louise Warhurst from GMP's Serious
OL,8,FCollision Investigation Unit said;
OL,9,F"Mansfield-Marr is a young man with a
OL,10,Ftruly appalling driving history, and
OL,11,Fhe bears full responsibility for this
OL,12,Ftragedy.
OL,14,F"During our investigation, we
OL,15,Funcovered a number of videos that were
OL,16,Ftaken on Mansfield-Marr's phone
OL,17,Fshowinghim driving dangerously at
OL,18,Fastonishing speeds.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
