OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,F"In one of the videos we found,
OL,8,FMansfield-Marr was driving at speeds
OL,9,Fexceeding 80mph on a motorway with his
OL,10,Ffeet crossed and resting out of the
OL,11,Fwindow while using cruise control.
OL,13,F"This is a dangerous man who believes
OL,14,Fthe rules and laws that all other road
OL,15,Fusers abide by daily do not apply to
OL,16,Fhim.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
