OL,3,C'He acted so brazenly, not caring he
OL,4,Ccould be caught': Driver kills
OL,5,Cpensioner
OL,7,F"At the time of the collision, he was
OL,8,Fa disqualified driver, but even that
OL,9,Fdid not deter him from driving
OL,10,Fdangerously and at speeds that were
OL,11,Fwholly inappropriate for the
OL,12,Fconditions.
OL,14,F"He acted so brazenly, not caring that
OL,15,Fhe could be caught.
